\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79a620d4eb00ef217ef76b1af2d441b45da8bd52","tid":1248071,"uid":39478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a37496a109252a31a65a7b3ec90f60a5772d6a31","tid":1248071,"uid":266688,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T11:08:55.000Z","msg":"你地咁樣圍個狗場真係好唔人道<br />\n人地都係打工既 比個機會人地放工好唔好?<br />\n其實圍警總既目標好撚清晰 反對克警使用過份武力<br />\n<br />\n所以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一定要成立獨立委員會調查</span></span>黎還克警們清白<br />\n咁有幾多克警使用過份武力姐<br />\n你地咁圍埋無辜既警狗唔岩架嘛<br />\n佢地清白架嘛?<br />\n佢地無罪架嘛?<br />\n無做過怕咩比人查?<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">局佢地支持成立獨立委員會調查咪可以放工LO</span></span><br />\n等佢地狗咬狗!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T11:50:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7a0f9c64ddf3beb9626e96c655f2eb023d35fe6a","tid":1248071,"uid":100016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T11:50:33.000Z","msg":"出黎認領啦喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96cbd0643f3c7d34336bf3a632f4834a4c31c213","tid":1248071,"uid":2837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T11:50:45.000Z","msg":"個post有聲"},{"pid":"74e8855f220a0032efb09789d93bedbb89b025d8","tid":1248071,"uid":138410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T11:54:20.000Z","msg":"前幾日經過灣仔狗場，見到好多黑狗一車車咁送入去，有好多隻流眼淚 佢地知就快俾人用完即棄...真係好慘!<br />\n<br />\n黑狗係無人性，幫共維穩....請大家唔好散水! 我都已經開始出門...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d82b36839549ac967a258601d091dac7de77a36","tid":1248071,"uid":15376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T11:56:26.000Z","msg":"狗樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b2f8145df0b4bc63be88ea09b7b08ca471d44f0","tid":1248071,"uid":88373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T11:56:26.000Z","msg":"捉晒去不人道毀滅"},{"p